{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I, you know, I stayed there for a year, which was essentially the school year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father, when he came to England, moved up into the area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't stay in London, where he certainly would have been re-arrested as an enemy alien, which is what the British did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even though they, they knew he, men were Jewish and, you know, they were afraid they were Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, look what we did to the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and he moved to near where I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he stayed at a YWCA, where he was a, a boarder, had little room there, and-- but I was sort of integrated into the school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I made a good friend-- English, couldn't be more English friend-- with whom I'm still in touch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And everybody was extremely kind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the, in the way-- I mean, everybody was kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "British boarding school system is-- has its own unkindnesses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this was not part of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents-- I, I don't recall the last night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I think my parents were much more conscious of the fact that we might never see each other again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, as I said, I, I thought it was an adventure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was not, I was not afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- it didn't occur to me that I might never see my parents again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how I could have been so innocent, but-- and I did see them again, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it, you know, it was just general excitement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was more excitement, I mean, for me, certainly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I recall my parents seeing me off and saying to my mother, don't cry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't cry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
